SIGNIFICANT MODIFICATIONS AND ADDITIONS BY DOCUMO:

The following features and enhancements have been added to the original codebase:

- Web dashboard with Vue.js frontend and FastAPI backend
- Authentication system (API Key and HTTP Basic Auth)
- Comprehensive audit logging with HMAC signing for compliance
- Modern CLI using Typer with rich output formatting
- Security hardening (input validation, command injection prevention)
- Pydantic-based configuration validation
- Rate limiting and CORS configuration
- Structured JSON logging
- Comprehensive test suite
- Renamed from CureIAM to IAMSentry

The original CureIAM project provided the foundational architecture for GCP IAM
recommendation scanning and processing, built upon the Cloudmarker framework.
